<author>Zalawma</author>
<title>Jerusalem Thak</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Van gam lopi tak chanchin,
 Kuo ahim a genthei ding ?
 Lungkhamna lei gimuma I len lai hin ?
 Hukdampa Isu Krista'n sinsak a hehpih kawmah,
 Van gam lopi zie chu a na hetsak tai

[V2]
 Aw van gam hawih leh nuom tak chu,
 Len guol kima kikhen lohna gam ahi;
 Hehpihna gam hawih zam vel,
 Lopina vak hawih zam vel,
 Keile tung ka, zie gam hawih leh nuomtak chu,

[V3]
 2. Zie khawpi vak hawih tak chu,
 A min Jerusalem thak;
 A khuo umna bang chu suongmantam ahi,
 Mi gen minthang sana leh dangka a zephawih ahi;
 A umna tuikawk suonga zephawih ahi.

[V4]
 3. Zie khawpi nuom tak achun,
 Nisa vak a ngai ta puoi;
 Tha leh aksi vak haw le ngai ta puona;
 Lalpa chu a vak hin tin, Ho In le um ta puona;
 Lalpa Isu mu'n Amah chu ho tai tiu.

[V5]
 4. A hehpihna leh phatna,
 Chu chawian in la sai tiu;
 Lungkhamna leh gitloh kihdak-umna haw,
 Kidona um ta puon tin In hawih lopi kawtkhak ah;
 Lalpa hehpihte mai chu lut thei unau.</lyrics>
</song>